headline: Q4 Earnings Outperformers: Fastenal (NASDAQ:FAST) And The Rest Of The Maintenance and Repair Distributors Stocks
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Fastenal (NASDAQ:FAST) and the best and worst performers in the maintenance and repair distributors industry.
